-- L’Oreal CEO Tells Investir Relations With Nestle Excellent
-- B y   A l b e r t i n a   T o r s o l i
-- 2013-04-20T10:36:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-20/l-oreal-ceo-tells-investir-relations-with-nestle-excellent.html
An evolution in the relations
between L’Oreal and Nestle, which owns almost 30 percent of
L’Oreal, “isn’t on the agenda for the time being,” L’Oreal CEO
Jean-Paul Agon told Investir in an interview published today.
* Relations with Nestle are “excellent,” L’Oreal CEO tells
French weekly newspaper
*L’Oreal to stick to acquisition strategy that will allow it to
buy new brands or to expand in foreign countries, Agon says
*NOTE: L’Oreal Rises in Paris as New Markets Help Sales Beat
